social_posts.post_text: Ok go off AI

I never really believed in signs before but after you passed, anytime I was outside or even just looking outside while thinking about you or talking about you, a butterfly would appear. I’ve never seen more monarchs in my garden. One time I said your name out loud and I swear the hugest butterfly I’ve ever seen in person flew above my head and hovered for a couple seconds before moving on. It always brought me peace, even if just for a fleeting moment.

I just wanted to have one of your butterflies with me anytime I needed a little help. Thank you @tomas_tumbleweed This one’s real special ❤️🦋

When my skin was at its worst last year, I feel like I put less effort into finding solutions because I honestly just didn't want to face it. Skin health is obviously not all about skincare; but when I started putting real effort into skincare again, it gave me the drive to address other aspects of my life that had been affecting my skin. It may seem strange but using @proactiv really kicked my butt into gear! I've been using the Proactiv MD line and recently started using their Skin Purifying Mask once a week. I am so pleased with my progress and I know it's just going to get even better from here!! #ad #proactivpartner

Is it really summertime if you haven’t gotten a backyard haircut?? 😎 My girl @ariannachayleneblean came over to lighten the weight & give my hair a lil more body/movement. We didn’t go too crazy with layers this time around b/c we wanted to see how this settles for now. 

I am so lazy when it comes to my hair (tbh it’s up in a pony/bun 90% of the time, especially in the summer) but I still want it look nice down (with minimal effort). I think it’s always important to be realistic with how much work you’re willing to put in - you may love a style but if it doesn’t fit with your lifestyle, it’s not gunna live up to the vision. With all that said, I’m looking forward to curling my hair now that it’s not all one length 😎😎

If you are local and looking to purchase gold, please go to the jewelers in Chinatown. They are not doing well at all and need our support. PLUS, they have THE BEST chains, pendants, etc.

#ad Josie has been eating @nutropetfood Natural Choice Adult Chicken & Brown Rice Recipe Dry Dog Food for a few months now! She’s never been very food motivated so it isn’t uncommon for her to leave food in her bowl all day. I knew Nutro was a winner when I was transitioning her to this food - she was gobbling up all the new Nutro kibble immediately and leaving the previous brands! 😅​

As a treat I will add Nutro’s So Simple Meal Complement Chicken Recipe in Bone Broth Grain-Free Adult Wet Dog Food Topper. I was so pleasantly surprised the first time I opened one of these up! You can clearly see all the ingredients and Josie LOVES that little quail egg. My sister’s maltipoo Mochi stayed with me for a few weeks and she is the pickiest eater - I started mixing some of this topper into her food and I’ve never seen her finish all of her food so fast every day!​
 
Like I said, I met the Nutro team recently and they truly are dog people who take great pride in utilizing high-quality ingredients in their food. I know that I’m giving Josie food that is good for her and that she loves to eat!!​#NUTROPartner
